    {
        "content": "<p>Can you also provide the code you used to get to your goal?</p>",
        "id": 558150435,
        "sender_full_name": "Riccardo Brasca",
        "timestamp": 1763544169
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>apply add_right_cancel (b := 0•w)<br>\nrw [zero_add]</p>",
        "id": 558151264,
        "sender_full_name": "Andrea Bourque",
        "timestamp": 1763544338
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>The problem is the line <code>add_right_cancel (b := 0•w)</code></p>",
        "id": 558152764,
        "sender_full_name": "Riccardo Brasca",
        "timestamp": 1763544811
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Lean thinks that <code>0</code> is the natural number <code>0</code></p>",
        "id": 558152801,
        "sender_full_name": "Riccardo Brasca",
        "timestamp": 1763544825
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>So after <code>apply add_right_cancel (b := 0•w)</code> the goal is</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">•</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">w</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">•</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">w</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">•</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">w</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>but the first <code>0</code> is in <code>K</code> and the second one is in <code>ℕ</code>, and now Lean is confused.</p>",
        "id": 558153272,
        "sender_full_name": "Riccardo Brasca",
        "timestamp": 1763544959
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>If you write</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">apply</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">add_right_cancel</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">K</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"bp\">•</span><span class=\"n\">w</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">rw</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">zero_add</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">smul_add</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>it works</p>",
        "id": 558154118,
        "sender_full_name": "Riccardo Brasca",
        "timestamp": 1763545202
    },
